{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781519154630,"sessionID":"ses_1352f6392ffeYuDqFBXc7h0kg7","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_01_KIOuUjNSm4kWkARzToHw1621","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/fanout-attribution.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/fanout-attribution.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Fan-Out Attribution\n2: \n3: Loop type: **research**  |  Lineage count: **2**\n4: \n5: | Label | Kind | Model | Iterations | Convergence | Salvaged | Verdict |\n6: |-------|------|-------|-----------|-------------|----------|---------|\n7: | codex-xhigh | unknown | unknown | 6 | 1 | 0 | n/a |\n8: | opus-account2 | unknown | unknown | 5 | n/a | 0 | n/a |\n\n(End of file - total 8 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Fan-Out Attribution\n\nLoop type: **research**  |  Lineage count: **2**\n\n| Label | Kind | Model | Iterations | Convergence | Salvaged | Verdict |\n|-------|------|-------|-----------|-------------|----------|---------|\n| codex-xhigh | unknown | unknown | 6 | 1 | 0 | n/a |\n| opus-account2 | unknown | unknown | 5 | n/a | 0 | n/a |","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/fanout-attribution.md","text":"# Fan-Out Attribution\n\nLoop type: **research**  |  Lineage count: **2**\n\n| Label | Kind | Model | Iterations | Convergence | Salvaged | Verdict |\n|-------|------|-------|-----------|-------------|----------|---------|\n| codex-xhigh | unknown | unknown | 6 | 1 | 0 | n/a |\n|