{"type":"text","timestamp":1781519181982,"sessionID":"ses_1352f6392ffeYuDqFBXc7h0kg7","part":{"id":"prt_ecad15d66001TTYBvGEPkpYJiH","messageID":"msg_ecad136fc001mv5Uv1xn70WCDR","sessionID":"ses_1352f6392ffeYuDqFBXc7h0kg7","type":"text","text":"Now I understand the landscape. The codex-xhigh lineage completed 6 iterations and converged. I need to set up and run the deepseek-v4-pro lineage independently from scratch, with max 5 iterations. Let me start with reading the external sources and setting up the init phase.","time":{"start":1781519179110,"end":1781519181980}}}
