"Initialize the charter, verify round-1 shipped set, establish the portability taxonomy.\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.95,\"noveltyJustification\":\"First pass established the portability taxonomy — a dimension neither sibling lineage assessed systematically — plus independent verification of the baseline, hook surface, agent count, and executor-config landing zone.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which fable-mode techniques are model-agnostic vs Anthropic-specific?\",\"What is the round-1 baseline?\",\"Where are the structural enforcement landing zones?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"What is the round-1 baseline?\",\"Where are the structural enforcement landing zones?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Re-recommend round-1's shipped set\",\"reason\":\"Out of scope per 002 spec\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/001-initial-refinement/before-vs-after.md:17\"},{\"approach\":\"Claim executor provenance fail-loud exists\",\"reason\":\"fallback-router handles quota exhaustion only; no model-mismatch verification path\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/fallback-router.ts:32-39\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-15T14:00:00Z\",\"durationMs\":0,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-deepseek-v4-pro-1781518620710-yepc7q\",\"generation\":1}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":2,\"run\":2,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"EXTRACT: Map every net-new technique from both sources, tagged with portability class, deduped vs round 1.\",\"findingsCount\":24,\"newInfoRatio\":0.72,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Systematically classified all 24 findings by portability for the first time: ~60% model-agnostic, ~25% Anthropic-specific, ~15% executor-portable. Separated efficiency-lever set (F10+G1:6-8+G5) from correctness-lever set (F1-F7,F11-F15).\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which techniques are model-agnostic vs Anthropic-specific?\",\"What is the efficiency core vs correctness core?\",\"Which dedup against round 1?\