rcement landing zones?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"What is the round-1 baseline?\",\"Where are the structural enforcement landing zones?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Re-recommend round-1's shipped set\",\"reason\":\"Out of scope per 002 spec\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/001-initial-refinement/before-vs-after.md:17\"},{\"approach\":\"Claim executor provenance fail-loud exists\",\"reason\":\"fallback-router handles quota exhaustion only; no model-mismatch verification path\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/fallback-router.ts:32-39\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-15T14:00:00Z\",\"durationMs\":0,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-deepseek-v4-pro-1781518620710-yepc7q\",\"generation\":1}\n+{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":2,\"run\":2,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"EXTRACT: Map every net-new technique from both sources, tagged with portability class, deduped vs round 1.\",\"findingsCount\":24,\"newInfoRatio\":0.72,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Systematically classified all 24 findings by portability for the first time: ~60% model-agnostic, ~25% Anthropic-specific, ~15% executor-portable. Separated efficiency-lever set (F10+G1:6-8+G5) from correctness-lever set (F1-F7,F11-F15).\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which techniques are model-agnostic vs Anthropic-specific?\",\"What is the efficiency core vs correctness core?\",\"Which dedup against round 1?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Which techniques are model-agnostic vs Anthropic-specific?\",\"What is the efficiency core vs correctness core?\",\"Which dedup against round 1?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Treating all governor rules as equally portable\",\"reason\":\"Rules 1-2 target Opus anxiety texture; non-Anthropic models don't have this failure mode\",\"evidence\":\"governor-block.md:1-7\"},{\"approach\":\"Porting G6 (caption test) as generic rule\",\"reason\":\"Targets thinking-block self-surveillance; non-thinking models lack equivalent\",\"evidence\":\"fable-mode.md:88-102\"},{\"approach\":\"Adopting F14 (ration live actions) for Public\",\"reason\":\"No shared production box; partially covered by name-the-rollback\",\"evidence\":\"fable-mode-profile.md:368-372\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-15T14:05:00Z\",\"durationMs\":0,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-deepseek-v4-pro-1781518620710-yepc7q\",\"generation\":1}\n","additions":1,"deletions":0},"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/deepseek-v4-pro/deep-research-state.jsonl","time":{"start":1781519405453,"end":1781519405455}},"id":"prt_ecad4a064001ZiDnDsXxmfSlgO","sessionID":"ses_1352f6392ffeYuDqFBXc7h0kg7","messageID":"msg_ecad494df001kLGUHJZ1LwmrBk"}}
