cation\":\"Introduced the B-structural vs B-advisory distinction — a load-bearing finding for implementation sequencing. Verified OpenCode lacks per-turn thermostat equivalent. Confirmed Codex hook file exists but wiring unconfirmed. Verified the dead pointer in AGENTS.md (cited file does not exist).\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which surfaces can structurally enforce vs advisory-only?\",\"Does OpenCode/Codex have hook-equivalent surfaces?\",\"What is the B-structural vs B-advisory distinction?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Which surfaces can structurally enforce vs advisory-only?\",\"Does OpenCode/Codex have hook-equivalent surfaces?\",\"What is the B-structural vs B-advisory distinction?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Rating OpenCode hook as HIGH\",\"reason\":\"No per-turn hook equivalent; hook briefs are session-start only\",\"evidence\":\"skill_advisor_hook.md (referenced file missing)\"},{\"approach\":\"Treating renderPromptPack as structural enforcement\",\"reason\":\"It injects text the agent can ignore; no behavioral verification path\",\"evidence\":\"post-dispatch-validate.ts:506-520\"},{\"approach\":\"Counting on OpenCode/Codex hook wiring without verification\",\"reason\":\"Codex hook file exists but settings.json wiring unconfirmed\",\"evidence\":\"grep: codex hook exists; wiring path not readable\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-15T14:10:00Z\",\"durationMs\":0,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-deepseek-v4-pro-1781518620710-yepc7q\",\"generation\":1}"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/deepseek-v4-pro/deep-research-state.jsonl\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/deepseek-v4-pro/deep-research-state.jsonl\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/deepseek-v4-pro/deep-research-state.jsonl\n@@ -1,3 +1,4 @@\n {\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Fable-5 efficiency: extract net-new fable-mode and opus-fable-mode mechanisms, map adjustable Public-repo surfaces by read reliability, and rank deduped surface x delta recommendations.\",\"maxIterations\":5,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"resource_map_present\":false,\"resource_map\":{\"emit\":true},\"createdAt\":\"2026-06-15T14:00:00Z\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research\",\"artifactDir\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/deepseek-v4-pro\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-deepseek-v4-pro-1781518620710-yepc7q\",\"generation\":1}\n {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":1,\"run\":1,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Initialize the charter, verify round-1 shipped set, establish the portability taxonomy.\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.95,\"noveltyJustification\":\"First pass established the portability taxonomy — a dimension neither sibling lineage assessed systematically — plus independent verification of the baseline, hook surface, agent count, and executor-config landing zone.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which fable-mode techniques are model-agnostic vs Anthropic-specific?\",\"What is the round-1 baseline?\",\"Where are the structural enforcement landing zones?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"What is the round-1 baseline?\",\"Where are the structural enforcement landing zones?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Re-recommend round-1's shipped set\",\"reason\":\"Out of scope per 002 spec\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/sk